overview: In the documentary The Court - Free or Folded? For the first time ever, we can follow behind the closed doors of a Swedish court. Never before has anyone filmed in court during a trial.Court - Free or folded? deals with everyday law, criminal law and litigation and you get an insight into how it works as a judge, prosecutor and lawyer. Those who come to court are from all walks of life. In front of the team, are we all equal?
